# CODEBOOK — Spend Smart or Spend Status?
### A Cross-Class Analysis of Consumer Buying Behaviour Towards Branded vs Unbranded Products in Mumbai

**Author:** Rishi Agrawal  
**Institution:** Shri Ramdeobaba College of Engineering and Management, Nagpur  
**GitHub:** [@HarshRi30](https://github.com/HarshRi30)

---

## Overview

This codebook documents the encoding applied to all columns in `Dataset for Spend Smart for postgresql.csv` — the cleaned, fully-encoded dataset derived from the raw Google Forms survey (`Spend Smart or Spend Status raw.csv`).

The preprocessing pipeline (`preprocessing.py`) transforms the raw 500-row export into a fully numeric, SQL-ready dataset. All multi-word string responses are mapped to compact integer codes; multi-select columns are exploded into binary dummy columns.

