### 4. Brand-as-Status Column

#### `branded_is_social_status`
*Survey question: "Do you believe branded products reflect social status?"*

| Code | Label |
|------|-------|
| 1 | No |
| 2 | Sometimes |
| 3 | Maybe |
| 4 | Yes |

> **Encoding note:** This column uses a 4-point ordinal scale (not a Likert scale). Higher values indicate stronger perception of branded products as a social status symbol. The ordering — No < Sometimes < Maybe < Yes — reflects ascending agreement with brand-as-status.

